msgid "walk off the end of"
msgstr "walk off the end of"

#: ../../W/walk-off-the-end-of.rst:7
msgid "vt\\."
msgstr "他動詞"

#: ../../W/walk-off-the-end-of.rst:9
msgid ""
"To run past the end of an array, list, or medium after stepping through it —"
" a good way to land in trouble. Often the result of an :ref:`off-by-one-"
"error`\\. Compare :ref:`clobber`\\, :ref:`roach`\\, :ref:`smash-the-"
"stack`\\."
msgstr ""
"配列、リスト、または媒体をたどり終えた後、その末尾を越えて走ること——トラブルに陥る格好の手立てだ。しばしば\\ :ref:`off-by-one-"
"error`\\ の結果である。\\ :ref:`clobber`\\ 、\\ :ref:`roach`\\ 、\\ :ref:`smash-the-"
"stack`\\ と比較せよ。"
